Cd1MLPgbVfU.title: International Ward in Tokuda Hospital Sofia opening ceremony
Cd1MLPgbVfU.description:
International Collaboration, Experience Exchange, and Best Practices:  

Our International Ward was created in collaboration between Tokuda Hospital Sofia, the Tokushukai Medical Group Japan, and Cambridge University Hospitals Addenbrookes from the UK all whom are on the management board of Tokuda Hospital Sofia to deliver innovative medical service and patient care excellence by global best health care practices from each partner organization.  

International Team:

Our International Ward personnel consists of multi-lingual nursing staff and physicians with international professional experience, whom have been additionally  trained to provide patient focused medical service based on specific cultural preferences and individualized patient needs.

Comprehensive and Multidisciplinary Diagnostics and Treatment: 

Our International Ward provides our patients full access to a wide spectrum of diagnostic and treatment services across our 30 plus medical specialties from cardiac surgery, interventional cardiology, neurology, neurosurgery, vascular surgery, CCSVI diagnostics and treatments, mini-invasive surgery (laparoscopic key-hole procedures), and many others. Our medical teams are dedicated to and routinely deliver multidisciplinary care via teams of specialists from different medical disciplines collaborating together based on the patient case to comprehensively treat complex medical conditions.

Increased Patient Access, Reduced Waiting Times, and International Specialists:  

Our International Ward is committed to increase patient access to innovative treatments by providing a platform for guest-doctors to provide treatments in our hospital. Thus patients can choose his/her specialist, can invite his physician from other hospitals, and/or even bring specialists from other countries to perform treatments in Tokuda taking full advantage of our excellent accommodation, assistance, and medical resources.

These features are the cornerstone of our International Ward namely to bring highly sought after specialists directly to patients in need.  This approach offers a rapid and convenient solution for patients in countries with long treatment waiting lists, for patients in need of innovative medical treatments not available in their countries, and or medical tourists looking for the best combination of comfort, price, and value.  Furthermore due to our convenient location between the Europe and Asia, we can significantly reduce travel time and travel expenses for medical tourists seeking treatment in more distant countries such as India or Thailand.

Hospital of Patient Choice:

Since our hospital began in 2006, we rapidly became the hospital of choice in Bulgaria for local and international patients. In 2011 alone, we delivered medical services to over 8,000 international patients including medical tourists whom traveled to Tokuda from the following countries/regions: 400 from the USA, 800 from Canada, 1,000 from the EU, 350 from Russia and the former Soviet republics, and over 200 from the Middle East.

In direct response to patient choice and the growing demand for our services, we created our International Ward to continue to develop as a preferred medical tourism destination offering high quality medical care and high patient value services at competitive pricing.
Accommodation Features and Comforts

Our International Department hospital rooms were individually designed to resemble hotel rooms each with its own design theme, color palettes, and matching furniture. Each room has been equipped with the following:

    Personal dressers and luggage storage areas
    Private bathroom with private bath or shower equipped with Japanese heated seat toilets with bidets
    Individual room heating and cooling with fully adjustable digital thermostats
    Fully electronically adjustable hospital beds
    Cable flat screen TVs
    Wireless internet access
    Spacious patient and visitor lounge with view of Vitosha Mountain
    Mini-refrigerators 

Patient Meals:

Another aspect of our tailored medical service is custom patient meals. We have a daily patient meal menu, which the patient can choose from international fare for various breakfast, lunch and dinner options. Of course these meal options are designed by a dietitian and designed with the patient's specific treatment, recovery process, and nutritional needs in mind in collaboration with the treating physician. Meals are delivered bedside, and they can also be ordered for patient companions and guests staying with or visiting the patient. 

For contacts: info@tokudabolnica.bg

Ob2-GUuz2Ag.title: Oobleck on a speaker
Ob2-GUuz2Ag.description:
Oobleck is a non-newtonian substance. A mixture of cornstarch and water. It's viscosity depends on the force that is applied to it. Treat it softly and it flows like a liquid. Hit it hard and it behaves like a solid. Just don't pour it down the drain, it will most likely cause a plug!

Imagination Station, Toledo's hands-on science center, is a vital non-profit organization that is an integral part of Toledo's economic, educational and social landscape. Imagination Station provides a critical layer of science enrichment by serving as an educational partner for teachers, schools and parents. It's with a thoughtful blend of exhibits, experiences, education and excitement that Imagination Station is inspiring future generations of scientists in Northwest Ohio. With more than 250 hands-on exhibits and demonstrations, Imagination Station delivers a multi-sensory experience that's as fun as it is educational.

Visit us at http://www.imaginationstationtoledo.org

Welcome to AutoMotoTube!!! On our channel we upload every day short, (2-5min) walkaround videos of Cars and Motorcycles. Our coverage is from Auto and Moto shows in North America and Europe - We visit different shows: Big, like Frankfurt, New York, Detroit, Los Angeles or Paris Auto Show, to small regional, Classic Car, RV and Boat Shows. 
We have thousands of High Definition videos of different types of vehicles, everything from new, concept cars, super cars, classic, vintage, old cars, hot rods, motorbikes, recreational vehicles, motor boats, sailing yachts, to airplanes, bicycles, and even tractors :-)
In most of our videos, we take a look at the exterior design and interior arrangements of the vehicle, so you can receive a general idea and appreciation of a certain brand or model.

We really appreciate all your comments and critics - they help a lot, in building one of the most diversified Auto & Vehicles Channel on YouTube!!!

P.S: To find a video of a certain model in our channel, just write the brand and model name in the search bar above, or have a look in our playlists.

enUi9tvsuQE.title: SDM 橡皮鴨游世界 - 香港站 2013年5月2日
enUi9tvsuQE.description:
期待已久的巨形鴨仔終於在海港城碼頭現身！
於當日早上SDM二十八位精靈可愛的學員穿著一身Duck Duck姿態的舞衣及加上精心的粧扮。老師及學員都為了開幕舞蹈表演做好準備功夫 。
為了要第一時間報導這件國際盛事，各大傳媒機構都霸佔有利位置。
大會更邀請SDM學員致送紀念品給主禮嘉賓。Duck爸爸霍夫曼及心晴行動主席林建明小姐看見和Rubber Duck一樣可愛的SDM 學員都想要和他們合照留念。
香港警察樂隊更以專業的步操管樂打開序幕，SDM學員可以與"Duck"共舞，真的是十分值得開心的一件事。就讓大家一起重温精彩的舞蹈表演片段！
